This paper is about sentiment analysis, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related topics. The paper also discusses various machine learning models, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of embeddings, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions benchmark datasets, which suggests that it could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) if the datasets involve images or multimedia content.
